summary: This mod replaces Serana with Elizabeth from Bioshock Infinite. The model was ported by yscsn!
descriptionHtml:
I guess this is my first mod so... yay!


Alright, so a while ago I found [url=https://yscsn.deviantart.com/art/Elizabeth-race-for-Skyrim-568664554]this Elizabeth port[/url] andÂ  I was using Familliar Faces to make her a follower. It got annoying and I've decided to finally take up modding and make this replacer.

This mod contains meshes and textures for the head and eyes aswell as custom hair from SGhairs.


It is incompatible with other Serana replacers.
If any problems arise, contact me and I will se what I can do :)


All credits to the maker of the mesh, yscsn, and the author of SGhairs!
author: Shepherd4
